Algorithme Signe_numbre

Variable n : Entier

Debut
    Ecrire("Enter an integer: ")
    Lire(n)

    // Check if the number is positive
    Si n > 0 Alors
        Ecrire("You entered a positive number: ", n, "\n")
    SinonSi n < 0 Alors
        Ecrire("You entered a negative number: ", n, "\n")
    Sinon
        Ecrire("You entered zero.\n")
    FinSi
Fin
